      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 29,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Data Flow:\n1. API receives scan request (local or GitHub) → 2. ScanService queries RAG for historical context → 3. If GitHub repo, fetch data via MCP GitHub Service → 4. Orchestrator Agent (LLM) decides which agents to run → 5. Agents execute in parallel → 6. LLM enhances outputs (release notes, suggestions, summaries) → 7. Optionally create GitHub issues from results → 8. Results stored in RAG → 9. Comprehensive report returned",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 140,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Data Flow:\n1. API receives scan request → 2. ScanService queries RAG for historical context → 3. Orchestrator Agent (LLM) decides which agents to run → 4. Agents execute in parallel → 5. LLM enhances outputs (release notes, suggestions, summaries) → 6. Results stored in RAG → 7. Comprehensive report returned"
    }
